ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR AI/ML COMPONENTS:

This project includes machine learning models and AI components. Users are 
encouraged to use this technology responsibly and ethically, particularly 
given its application in accessibility and communication assistance.

The authors strongly encourage:
- Respect for privacy and consent when processing video data
- Consideration of the deaf and hard-of-hearing community's needs
- Responsible deployment in production environments
- Proper attribution when building upon this work

For questions about commercial use or licensing, please contact the maintainers.